Description:
Entertainers Paradise!
If you love to entertain and want room to move, then this home is for you. The outdoor entertaining area alone offers a built in bar, lounge and dining areas and even has room for the pool table! It has built in sink and solid fuel heater for those cold winter nights and has bistro blinds that drop down making it usable all year round. It is truly a sensational space! Move inside you will find a stunning kitchen which boasts stainless steel appliances and so much cupboard space! There are 2-3 living zones internally with an oversized sunken lounge to the front of the home and a separate rumpus room to the rear. The kitchen overlooks the dining/family room which then steps out to alfresco living. There are three bedrooms plus study in total with the master suite located to the rear of the home with its own luxurious bathroom suite with bath, separate shower, separate toilet and oversized vanity. It also boasts large walk in robe located behind mirrored sliding robe doors. Climate throughout is controlled by gas ducted heating and evaporative cooling. The double garage again is spacious in size and has direct access into the home. Externally there is a huge shed which is approximately 10.5m long x 12m wide with an additional 3m lean to. The roof is quite high to the shed allowing for higher roller doors to allow for boats/caravans. This home positioned on 1.8 acres of land and is a must for viewing and will not disappoint!
Statement of information can be found at https://property-soi.mydesktop.com.au/27980/16975272/Statement+of+information+-+1+Catona+Crescent%2C+COBRAM+-+08d63007-1a26-4cff-a30e-b52315548bef.pdf

Description:
Handy Location ~ Great Shed!
Very well presented three bedroom home set on a peaceful two acres (approx.) and only a short drive to Cobram. The home features a new kitchen with electric cooking and skylight and a comfortable lounge with a split system air conditioner. Three generous bedrooms, two with built in robes, main with its own split system air conditioner, and all with ceiling fans. Front verandah, fernery and double carport. Huge 8 metre by 15 metre (approx.) lockup shed with large sliding doors, work benches, concrete floor, 3 phase power, water, stove, solid fuel heater - the perfect workshop/man cave!. Delightful surrounds, fruit trees, vegie garden, two large water tanks plus 2 megs stock and domestic water. 12 panel solar electricity system. Sundry shedding.
Excellent low maintenance property with space to relax. Arrange your inspection now!

Address: Lot 2 - 6091 Tocumwal Benalla Road Cobram VIC 3644
Description:
ESTABISHED LUCERNE PROPERTY & EXCELLENT SOILS
This is an outstanding parcel of land with extremely fertile soil types and perfect for growing Lucerne.
276 Acres-111.74 Hectares, one title with established Lucerne of (approx) 150 acres 60.72 Hectares and (approx) 126 acres -51 hectares of Silver Gums.
The 150 acres has been completely lasered (approx) 2 years ago with well laid bays and an excellent drainage system. Irrigating is made easy with the installation of Padman stops which are either 6ft or 8ft wide.
This is a fantastic opportunity for someone wanting to continue growing Lucerne supplying to the local and interstate markets. The property is also ideal for grazing cattle or sheep.
Irrigation water is supplied by a backbone channel from Goulburn Murray Water with delivery shares in place.
The balance of the land of (approx) 126 acres has established Silver Gum trees which are harvested on a regular basis and have been supplying to the florist market for (approx) 15 years. The Silver Gums are an ongoing business with extremely good returns.
